OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FPeter Mandelson reportedly failed his
OL,8,Fsecurity vetting process before taking
OL,9,Fup the role of Washington ambassador,
OL,10,Fbut the decision was overruled by the
OL,11,FForeign Office, according to an
OL,12,Finvestigation by The Guardian.
OL,14,FMultiple sources told the paper that
OL,15,F"Mandelson was initially denied
OL,16,Fclearance in late January 2025 after a
OL,17,Fdeveloped vetting process, a highly
OL,18,Fconfidential background check by
OL,19,Fsecurity officials."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
