CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776395018
OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FThis occurred after Prime Minister Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer had announced his
OL,9,Fappointment, saying in December 2024
OL,10,Fthat he was "delighted to appoint" him
OL,11,Fas UK ambassador to the US, adding:
OL,12,F"Peter will bring unrivalled
OL,13,Fexperience to the role."
OL,15,FThe Guardian reports the Foreign
OL,16,FOffice decided to reach for "a rarely
OL,17,Fused authority to override the
OL,18,Frecommendation from security
OL,19,Fofficials."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776395018
OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FIt is not known if the PM was aware
OL,8,Fthat Mandelson had in fact failed
OL,9,Fsecurity vetting when Starmer said
OL,10,Fduring a press conference in Hastings
OL,11,Fin February 2025 that he had been
OL,12,Fgiven "clearance for the role."
OL,14,FIt is also unknown who at the Foreign
OL,15,FOffice decided to overrule UK Security
OL,16,FVetting's recommendation against
OL,17,FMandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
