OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FAt the time of this decision, the
OL,8,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy was
OL,9,Fthe Foreign Secretary, with Olly
OL,10,FRobbins serving as the chief civil
OL,11,Fservant in the department.
OL,13,FThe current Foreign Secretary, Yvette
OL,14,FCooper herself, alongside Robbins,
OL,15,Fwrote to the Foreign Affairs Select
OL,16,FCommittee in September 2025 saying:
OL,17,F"Peter Mandelson's security vetting
OL,18,Fwas conducted to the usual standard
OL,19,Fset for developed vetting in line with
OL,20,Festablished Cabinet Office policy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
