OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FThey wrote that this "concluded with
OL,8,FDV clearance being granted by the
OL,9,FFCDO."
OL,11,FMandelson was sacked as Washington
OL,12,Fambassador earlier this year after
OL,13,Frevelations came to light about his
OL,14,Fclose relationship with the paedophile
OL,15,Ffinancier, Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
