OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FResponding at the time, a lawyer
OL,8,Frepresenting Mandelson issued a
OL,9,Fstatement claiming: "The arrest was
OL,10,Fprompted by a baseless suggestion that
OL,11,Fhe was planning to leave the country
OL,12,Fand take up permanent residence
OL,13,Fabroad. There is absolutely no truth
OL,14,Fwhatsoever in any such suggestion."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
