OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FMandelson has previously apologised
OL,8,Ffor his relationship with Epstein,
OL,9,Fclaiming he did not witness wrongdoing
OL,10,Fin his interactions with the
OL,11,Fpaedophile and "deeply regrets"
OL,12,Fcontinuing his relationship for so
OL,13,Flong.
OL,15,FIn relation to his arrest on suspicion
OL,16,Fof misconduct in public office, the
OL,17,Fformer ambassador claims not to have
OL,18,Facted in any way criminally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
