OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FQuestions have been asked of senior
OL,8,Fofficials and the prime minister over
OL,9,Fwhat they knew when during Mandelson's
OL,10,Fappointment, with MPs forcing the
OL,11,Fpublication of hundreds of documents
OL,12,Frelating to this process.
OL,14,FThe first tranche of these documents
OL,15,Fwas released in March, with many more
OL,16,Fexpected to follow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
