OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FThese files revealed Mandelson had
OL,8,Freceived "high-tier" briefings before
OL,9,Fhis vetting process was complete, as
OL,10,Fwell as showing the prime minister had
OL,11,Fknown about Mandelson's continued
OL,12,Frelationship with Epstein when he made
OL,13,Fthe appointment.
OL,15,FA timeline of events between Peter
OL,16,FMandelson and paedophile Jeffrey
OL,17,FEpstein.
OL,19,FCan't see this timeline on your mobile
OL,20,Fdevice? Click here to open it in
OL,21,Fbrowser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
