OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FIn September 2025, during a call
OL,8,Fbetween Starmer's general counsel and
OL,9,Fthe then-national security adviser,
OL,10,FJonathan Powell, the latter said he
OL,11,Ffound the appointment of Mandelson
OL,12,F"weirdly rushed".
OL,14,FPowell goes on to say he raised the
OL,15,Fconcerns he has with the PM's chief of
OL,16,Fstaff, Morgan McSweeney, but was told
OL,17,Fthey had been addressed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
