CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776395018
OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FPowell also notes that the then junior
OL,8,Fminister in the Foreign Office,
OL,9,FPhillip Barton, also had reservations
OL,10,Fabout Mandelson's appointment.
OL,12,FMcSweeney was forced to resign in
OL,13,FFebruary after Mandelson's
OL,14,Fappointment, saying at the time he
OL,15,Ftook "full responsibility" for
OL,16,Fadvising the PM to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
