OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FResponding to the report by the
OL,8,FGuardian, Tory leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,9,Fsaid: "Last September, Keir Starmer
OL,10,Ftold parliament three times that 'full
OL,11,Fdue process' was followed over the
OL,12,Fappointment of Lord Mandelson.
OL,14,F"We now know the prime minister misled
OL,15,Fthe House. The prime minister must
OL,16,Ftake responsibility."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
