OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FLib Dem leader Ed Davey called for
OL,8,FStarmer's resignation if he "misled
OL,9,Fparliament and lied to the British
OL,10,Fpublic" over Lord Peter Mandelson's
OL,11,Fvetting as US ambassador.
OL,13,FDavey said: "Keir Starmer had already
OL,14,Fmade a catastrophic error of judgment.
OL,15,FNow it looks as though he has also
OL,16,Fmisled parliament and lied to the
OL,17,FBritish public. If that is the case,
OL,18,Fhe must go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
