OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776395018
OL,3,CMandelson reportedly failed vetting
OL,4,Cbut decision was overruled by Foreign
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,F"Labour came into government on a
OL,8,Fpromise to clean up politics. Instead,
OL,9,Fwe're seeing the same old sleaze,
OL,10,Fscandal and cover-ups as we did under
OL,11,Fthe Conservatives."
OL,13,FThe Green Party has also called for
OL,14,FStarmer's resignation, with MP Sian
OL,15,FBerry saying: "Keir Starmer has lied
OL,16,Fand lied again over his decision to
OL,17,Fappoint Peter Mandelson and he must
OL,18,Fresign.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
